'''自慰'''，又称'''自渎'''<ref name="家計會教育組 2012"/><ref name="刘达临 1993">{{Cite book|author=刘达临|title=中华性学辞典|publisher=黑龙江人民出版社|year=1993|accessdate=2016-07-25|pages=386|isbn=7-207-02609-9|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=7xgRAQAAMAAJ&q=挊+手淫&dq=挊+手淫&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&redir_esc=y|quote=手淫又叫自慰、自渎或自抚,指个人采用某种方法刺激自己的身体以达到性快感或性高潮,因通常用手去做,故叫手淫。女性會用手插入陰莖並且來會插入|archive-date=2020-09-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200917145220/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=7xgRAQAAMAAJ&q=%E6%8C%8A+%E6%89%8B%E6%B7%AB&dq=%E6%8C%8A+%E6%89%8B%E6%B7%AB&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&redir_esc=y|dead-url=no}}</ref>、'''自淫'''、'''手淫'''<ref name="家計會教育組 2012"/><ref name="刘达临 1993"/>，是指对自己[[性器官|性器官]]進行[[性刺激|性刺激]]，而达到[[性兴奋|性兴奋]]和[[性高潮|性高潮]]、获得[[性快感|性快感]]的[[人类性行为|性行為]]<ref name="家計會教育組 2012"/><ref name="webmd">{{cite web |url=http://www.webmd.com/sex-relationships/guide/masturbation-guide |title=Masturbation - Is Masturbation Normal or Harmful? Who Masturbates? Why Do People Masturbate? |publisher=Webmd.com |date=2010-03-04 |accessdate=2011-08-17 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161121045511/http://www.webmd.com/sex-relationships/guide/masturbation-guide |archivedate=2016-11-21 }}</ref>。自慰時可能用手、手指、日常物品或專門的[[性玩具|性玩具]]等來進行性刺激<ref name="家計會教育組 2012"/><ref name="webmd" /><ref>Based on "masturbation" in ''Merriam-Webster's Collegiate Dictionary, Eleventh Edition'', Merriam-Webster, Inc., 2003</ref>。伴侶間互相刺激性器官的行為稱為[[非插入式性行為|相互抚慰]]，可取代[[插入式性行為|插入式性行為]]。研究發現自慰雖然有各種不同形式，但皆為普遍存在的人類行為，無分性別與年紀<ref name="香港家庭計劃指導會">{{cite web|url=https://www.famplan.org.hk/zh/our-services/e-services/sex-qa/index/puberty/masturbation/detail|title=自慰|publisher=香港家庭計劃指導會|accessdate=2017-04-22|archive-date=2021-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210405023340/https://www.famplan.org.hk/zh/our-services/e-services/sex-qa/index/puberty/masturbation/detail|dead-url=no}}</ref>，雖然頻率會有變化。“淫”在中文中有「過多」、「沉迷」和「不正當」的意思<ref>{{cite web|title =淫的解釋 淫的意思|publisher =漢典|date =|url =http://www.zdic.net/z/1d/js/6DEB.htm|accessdate =2016-07-25|deadurl =no|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160929053427/http://www.zdic.net/z/1d/js/6DEB.htm|archivedate =2016-09-29|quote =字义：1. 过多……4. 在男女关系上态度或行为不正当……5. 放纵，沉溺}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|author=|title=常用新辭典|publisher=商務印書館(香港)有限公司|year = 1989|pages= 431|isbn=962-07-0002-3|quote=①过量的……②不正当的}}</ref>，「瀆」則有「不尊重」的意思<ref>{{cite web|title =瀆的解釋 瀆的意思|publisher =漢典|date =|url =http://www.zdic.net/z/1d/js/6E0E.htm|accessdate =2016-07-25|deadurl =no|archiveurl =https://web.archive.org/web/20160929053430/http://www.zdic.net/z/1d/js/6E0E.htm|archivedate =2016-09-29|quote =字义：……2. 轻慢，对人不恭敬}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book|author=|title=中華新字典|publisher=中華書局|year = 1990|pages= 316|isbn=962-231-001-X|quote=瀆……②褻瀆，輕慢，對人不恭敬}}</ref>，都屬于[[貶義|貶義]]詞，故此現代比較傾向稱其為自慰<ref name="家計會教育組 2012"/>，因為科學家並未發現適當的自慰與任何形式的心理或生理異常之間有關<ref name="家計會教育組 2012"/><ref>{{cite book |last1=Coleman |first1=Eli |year=2012 |orig-year=2002 |chapter=Masturbation as a Means of Achieving Sexual Health |chapterurl=http://samples.sainsburysebooks.co.uk/9781317787587_sample_833458.pdf |chapter-format=PDF |editor1-last=Bockting |editor1-first=Walter O. |editor2-last=Coleman |editor2-first=Eli |title=Masturbation as a Means of Achieving Sexual Health |url= |location=New York |publisher=Routledge, Taylor & Francis Group |publication-date= |page=7 |pages= |at= |nopp= |isbn=0-7890-2047-5 |oclc=50913590 |quote=Despite the scientific evidence indicating that masturbation is generally a normal variant of sexual expression and that it does not seem to have a causal relationship with sexual pathology, negative attitudes about masturbation persist and it remains stigmatized. |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161121071454/http://samples.sainsburysebooks.co.uk/9781317787587_sample_833458.pdf |archivedate=2016-11-21 |access-date=2016-07-16 }}</ref>。

自史前時代開始，許多藝術和文學作品就已有關於自慰的描繪。在18和19世紀時，部分歐洲的神學家和醫生曾用「可憎」、「可悲」和「醜陋」來形容自慰行為，但到了20世紀，將自慰視為[[禁忌|禁忌]]的觀念已經逐漸不復存在。在藝術、流行音樂、電視、電影和文學中對於自慰的討論和描繪持續增加。各宗教間對於自慰則有不同見解，有些宗教認為自慰會造成靈性層面的傷害，有些宗教則認為自慰在靈性層面上並無害，而亦有宗教對自慰採用{{le|情境道德|Situational ethics}}的觀點。從古至今，自慰的合法性也經過多次變遷，而公開自慰在現今大多數的國家屬違法行為。<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Hallikeri|first1=Vinay R.|last2=Gouda|first2=Hareesh.|last3=Aramani|first3=Sunil C.|last4=Vijaykumar|first4=A.G.|last5=Ajaykumar|first5=T.S.|date=2010-07-12|title=MASTURBATION—AN OVERVIEW|url=http://www.jfmtonline.org/current/masterbation_an_overview.php|journal=Journal of Forensic Medicine and Toxicology|location=New Delhi|publisher=Medicolegal Society|volume=27|issue=2|pages=46–49|issn=0971-1929|quote=Today, masturbatory act is considered as a healthy practice when done in private and an offence if done in the public in most of the countries.|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821082841/http://www.jfmtonline.org/current/masterbation_an_overview.php|archivedate=2016-08-21|access-date=2014-02-26}}</ref>

在[[西方世界|西方世界]]，私下或與伴侶間的自慰通常被認為是健康正常的[[性健康|性健康]]，許多正式的醫療機構也在宣傳折頁或政策中表達同樣的看法。科學家也觀察到不同物種的許多動物亦有自慰行為<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.petplace.com/horses/breeding-soundness-examination-of-the-stallion/page2.aspx |title=Breeding Soundness Examination of the Stallion |publisher=Petplace.com |accessdate=2011-05-29 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110905032903/http://www.petplace.com/horses/breeding-soundness-examination-of-the-stallion/page2.aspx |archivedate=2011-09-05 }}</ref><ref name="Bagemihl,1999">{{cite book |author=Bagemihl, Bruce |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=5CbRGV8AAIQC&printsec=frontcover#v=snippet&q=masturbation&f=false |title=Biological Exuberance: Animal Homosexuality and Natural Diversity |publisher=St. Martin's Press |year=1999 |isbn=0-312-19239-8 |accessdate=2015-10-21 |archive-date=2021-04-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210405023403/https://books.google.com/books?id=5CbRGV8AAIQC&printsec=frontcover#v=snippet&q=masturbation&f=false |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>For further references, see also the main article {{le|Animal sexuality#Autoeroticism (masturbation)|Animal sexuality#Autoeroticism (masturbation)}}.</ref>。

==詞源==
自慰的英語「masturbation」在18世紀便為人使用，其是由拉丁文「masturbari」演變而來，與更專門及更早出現的「onanism」並用。拉丁文動詞「masturbari」的來源並未確定，但據推測為陰莖「mazdo」的同義詞，其與希臘文中的生殖器「mézea μέζεα」相近。或是「manusturpare」（用手污瀆）的变体，但此說法未曾證實。<ref>{{cite book |last=Dally |first=Peter |title=The Fantasy Factor |year=1975 |page=135 |publisher=George Weidenfeld and Nicolson Limited |isbn=0-297-76945-6}}</ref><ref>''OED'', s.v. ''[http://oed.com/view/Entry/114847 masturbation]{{subscription required}}''</ref>

「手淫」一词源于何时尚待考证，光绪二十五年十月（1899年）在上海刻印的刘仲衡著作《中西汇参铜人图说》便有提到「若手淫自泄，伤身更甚，每有青盲聋懵之症」<ref name="陶林">{{cite web|title=“手淫”一词该变成“自慰”吗|url=http://www.zgxkx.org/sex/xxpl/201104/615.html|publisher=中国性科学|author=陶林|date=2011-04-29|accessdate=2016-11-24|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161125043609/http://www.zgxkx.org/sex/xxpl/201104/615.html|archivedate=2016-11-25}}</ref>。「自慰」一詞則由日本的生物學家{{link-ja|山本宣治|山本宣治}}及性學家{{link-ja|小倉清三郎|小倉清三郎}}為去除污名化而提出<ref name="劉黎兒"/>，其後，漢字文化圈便廣泛應用之<ref name="劉黎兒">{{cite news|author=劉黎兒|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/forum/20091112/32084190/|title=自慰是山本想出來的|publisher=蘋果日報|date=2009-11-12|accessdate=2016-11-24|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161125044134/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/appledaily/article/forum/20091112/32084190/|archivedate=2016-11-25}}</ref>，很多性学家都推荐使用「自慰」一詞<ref name="陶林"/>。

