活習慣<ref name="Telegraph 2009">{{cite web|url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/5806691/NHS-tells-school-children-of-their-right-to-an-orgasm-a-day.html|title=NHS tells school children of their "right" to "an orgasm a day"|author=Roya Nikkhah|publisher=Telegraph|date=2009-07-12|accessdate=2015-10-08|deadurl=no|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161227003026/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/education/5806691/NHS-tells-school-children-of-their-right-to-an-orgasm-a-day.html|archivedate=2016-12-27}}</ref>。

