dromes|url=http://www.medscape.com/features/slideshow/culture-synd#14|author=Christoph U. Correll, MD；Bret S. Stetka, MD|quote=...In shenkui, marked anxiety or panic symptoms are accompanied by somatic complaints, such as dizziness, backache, fatigue, and complaints of sexual dysfunction. The excessive loss of semen is feared because it is seen as the loss of one's vital essence.|accessdate=2017-01-02|publisher=medscape|archive-date=2020-04-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200420164358/https://www.medscape.com/features/slideshow/culture-synd#14|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last1=Semple|first1=Semple|last2=Smyth|first2=Roger|title=Oxford Handbook of Psychiatry|page=920|publisher=Oxford University Press|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=5h9FAgAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=Oxford+Handbook+of+Psychiatry&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjlyfKsysDWAhVIzLwKHcUBBmUQ6AEIJTAA#v=onepage&q=Oxford%20Handbook%20of%20Psychiatry&f=false|isbn=978-0-19-969388-7|year=2013|access-date=2017-09-25|archive-date=2021-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210405024000/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=5h9FAgAAQBAJ&printsec=frontcover&dq=Oxford+Handbook+of+Psychiatry&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjlyfKsysDWAhVIzLwKHcUBBmUQ6AEIJTAA#v=onepage&q=Oxford%20Handbook%20of%20Psychiatry&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="umathipala, A. 2004"/><ref name="DSM 5">{{Cite book|title=Diagnostic and Statistical Manual of Mental Disorders, 5th Edition|publisher=[[American_Psychiatric_Association|American Psychiatric Publishing]]|url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=-JivBAAAQBAJ&pg=PT1434&lpg=PT1434&dq=Dhat+syndrome+is+a+term+that+was+coined+in+South+Asia+little+more+than+half+a+century+ago+to+account+for+common+clinical+presentations+of+young+male+patients+who+attributed+their+various+symptoms+to+semen+loss.&source=bl&ots=ceNN37JMAb&sig=Mv3tHEkCF8LwvwOGELP6U1ksqQo&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjExfbdgvDVAhVB2LwKHX4uDbAQ6AEIMjAC#v=onepage&q=Dhat%20syndrome%20is%20a%20term%20that%20was%20coined%20in%20South%20Asia%20little%20more%20than%20half%20a%20century%20ago%20to%20account%20for%20common%20clinical%20presentations%20of%20young%20male%20patients%20who%20attributed%20their%20various%20symptoms%20to%20semen%20loss.&f=false|year=2013|accessdate=2017-08-24|archive-date=2021-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210405023935/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=-JivBAAAQBAJ&pg=PT1434&lpg=PT1434&dq=Dhat+syndrome+is+a+term+that+was+coined+in+South+Asia+little+more+than+half+a+century+ago+to+account+for+common+clinical+presentations+of+young+male+patients+who+attributed+their+various+symptoms+to+semen+loss.&source=bl&ots=ceNN37JMAb&sig=Mv3tHEkCF8LwvwOGELP6U1ksqQo&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwjExfbdgvDVAhVB2LwKHX4uDbAQ6AEIMjAC#v=onepage&q=Dhat%20syndrome%20is%20a%20term%20that%20was%20coined%20in%20South%20Asia%20little%20more%20than%20half%20a%20century%20ago%20to%20account%20for%20common%20clinical%20presentations%20of%20young%20male%20patients%20who%20attributed%20their%20various%20symptoms%20to%20semen%20loss.&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite encyclopedia|last=Ninnemann|first=K|year=2012|title=Shenkui|encyclopedia=In Encyclopedia of Immigrant Health|pages=1350|publisher=Springer New York|url=http://link.springer.com/referenceworkentry/10.1007%2F978-1-4419-5659-0_700|access-date=2017-01-02|archive-date=2021-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210405023940/https://link.springer.com/referenceworkentry/10.1007%2F978-1-4419-5659-0_700|dead-url=no}}</ref>，是由對「精」損耗的焦慮<ref name="ICD"/><ref name="cause and explain"/><ref name="umathipala, A. 2004">{{cite journal|last1=Sumathipala|first1=A|last2=Siribaddana|first2=S. H.|last3=Bhugra|first3=D|year=2004|title=Culture-bound syndromes: the story of dhat syndrome|journal=The British Journal of Psychiatry|volume=184|issue=3|pages=200-209|url=http://bjp.rcpsych.org/content/184/3/200.long|pmid=14990517|doi=10.1192/bjp.184.3.200|access-date=2017-09-25|archive-date=2013-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130322043257/http://bjp.rcpsych.org/content/184/3/200.long|dead-url=yes}}</ref>及疑病<ref name="cause and explain"/>導致。據文榮光及王經綸於1977年7月至11月間在台灣進行的研究顯示：没有性功能障礙的肾虛病例中，病患的精神病理達至精神官能症的水準，且都被診斷出不同的心理問題<ref name="文榮光、王經綸1990"/><ref name="umathipala, A. 2004"/>。

