===一般好處===
性治療師有時會建議女性患者花時間來相互抚慰達到高潮，以幫助提高性健康和關係，因為相互抚慰可令性關係更令人滿意和增加親切感<ref name="Shuman06">{{cite web |last = Shuman |first = Tracy |title = Your Guide to Masturbation |publisher = WebMD, Inc./The Cleveland Clinic Department of Obstetrics and Gynecology |date = 2006-02 |url = http://www.webmd.com/sex-relationships/guide/masturbation-guide |accessdate = 2006-07-29 |deadurl = no |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20170101102055/http://www.webmd.com/sex-relationships/guide/masturbation-guide |archivedate = 2017-01-01 }}</ref><ref name="Knowles02">{{cite web |last = Knowles |first = Jon |title = Masturbation — From Stigma to Sexual Health |publisher = Katharine Dexter McCormick Library/Planned Parenthood Federation of America, Inc. |date = 2002-11 |url = https://www.plannedparenthood.org/files/5513/9611/7867/masturbation_11-02.pdf |accessdate = 2006-07-29 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20161201170718/https://www.plannedparenthood.org/files/5513/9611/7867/masturbation_11-02.pdf |archivedate = 2016-12-01 }}</ref>。

許多精神衛生界人士認為自慰可以緩解[[重性抑郁障碍|抑鬱]]並提高[[自尊|自尊]]<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.healthline.com/galecontent/masturbation-1 |title=Masturbation Information on Healthline |publisher=Healthline.com |accessdate=2011-08-17 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130430122448/http://www.healthline.com/galecontent/masturbation-1 |archivedate=2013-04-30 }}</ref>。自慰也在其中一個伴侣的性需要較另一方多時格外有幫助，在這種情況下自慰提供了一個平衡的作用，因而關係能更和諧<ref name="BadgerHerald">{{cite web |title = Masturbation key to healthy, functional sexual relationships |date = 2007-04-19 |url = http://badgerherald.com/oped/2007/04/19/masturbation-key-to/ |work = The Badger Herald, Daily campus newspaper |location = Madison, Wisconsin, USA |publisher = Badger Herald, Inc. |accessdate = 2007-07 |deadurl = yes |archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141006132308/http://badgerherald.com/oped/2007/04/19/masturbation-key-to/ |archivedate = 2014-10-06 }}</ref>。

相互抚慰，通過觀察一個伴侣手淫，可以找出怎樣才能取悦對方。性交本身往往是不方便或不可行去使大部分人得到足夠的性釋放，相互抚慰能令夫妻互相享受和獲得性釋放，但沒有不便和相關風險<ref name="BadgerHerald" />。

对于自慰与[[前列腺癌|前列腺癌]]患病风险的关系，主流医学界偏向于自慰對其有益或无关<ref>{{cite news|title=手淫引起前列腺癌？吓得我赶紧缩回了手...|url=https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MTg0MzMwODA0MQ==&mid=2653342319&idx=1&sn=3ff3273ffe59c0b384240b3e900341fc&chksm=5e333b096944b21f09f8c06913e92200ab4fde9a2ebb2a90ec78bf6542a6f3184e96f6a44665&mpshare=1&scene=1&srcid=1214kYorneruZLkdRG4PTCMh&pass_ticket=v0VjPnfhf7MuVau6Um%2FZBMJ%2F37qThkcLtgHi8Z8puH5qxqvxBqDeMOtYVHiARnqk#rd|accessdate=2017-12-14|publisher=丁香园|date=2017-12-14}}</ref>。

