一个研究显示，一组只有性交经验的人的[[血压|血压]]比另一组在性交的同时也进行一次或多次自慰的人的血压要低<ref>{{cite journal |author=Brody S |title=Blood pressure reactivity to stress is better for people who recently had penile-vaginal intercourse than for people who had other or no sexual activity |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_biological-psychology_2006-02_71_2/page/214 |journal=Biol Psychol |volume=71 |issue=2 |pages=214–22 |date=2006-02 |pmid=15961213 |doi=10.1016/j.biopsycho.2005.03.005}}</ref>。

